What do you say?

00:02:01.480 --> 00:02:02.920
You can send her home,

00:02:03.160 --> 00:02:04.440
but don't take advantage of her.

00:02:05.440 --> 00:02:06.720
Of course.

00:02:10.214 --> 00:02:11.120
Ms. Man Li.

00:02:12.640 --> 00:02:13.360
Wake up.

00:02:15.120 --> 00:02:17.040
Go home and sleep it off.

00:02:19.360 --> 00:02:20.480
Easy now.

