00:02:47.120 --> 00:02:48.520
Yamamoto sent her home.

00:02:49.760 --> 00:02:51.160
He also gave a generous gift.

00:02:51.160 --> 00:02:52.480
We'll enjoy it later.

00:02:53.040 --> 00:02:53.800
What gift?

00:02:54.400 --> 00:02:55.490
You'll see when we get back.

00:02:59.200 --> 00:03:01.200
