00:03:02.760 --> 00:03:03.960
A little.

00:03:13.120 --> 00:03:14.400
You know this.

00:03:14.880 --> 00:03:16.000
People like us

00:03:16.000 --> 00:03:18.000
shouldn't get involved in relationships.

00:03:18.460 --> 00:03:21.200
What's more, Zhou Musheng's
with the North City Chamber of Commerce.

00:03:21.720 --> 00:03:23.040
He's unreliable.

00:03:24.160 --> 00:03:25.320
But Hong,

00:03:26.880 --> 00:03:28.800
I think he's different from the rest.

00:03:30.680 --> 00:03:31.680
Different how?

00:03:32.220 --> 00:03:33.840
Birds of a feather,
they're all the same.

00:03:34.160 --> 00:03:35.520
He's maybe just better looking.

00:03:38.440 --> 00:03:40.920
(Should I really not let myself
fall for him?)

00:03:42.920 --> 00:03:43.760
Hong,

00:03:44.080 --> 00:03:46.440
I'm craving cake from Yangtze Hotel.

00:03:46.440 --> 00:03:47.480
Let's go buy some.

00:03:47.680 --> 00:03:49.360
You'll get fat.

00:03:49.640 --> 00:03:51.360
Hong, you're the best.

00:03:52.240 --> 00:03:53.320
You're such a handful.

00:04:05.120 --> 00:04:06.680
Oh, my little darling.

00:04:08.400 --> 00:04:09.640
You smell so nice.

00:04:12.440 --> 00:04:14.920
You're a feisty one.

00:04:14.920 --> 00:04:16.040
I like that.

00:04:18.000 --> 00:04:19.440
Oh, darling.

00:04:19.440 --> 00:04:21.160
We're almost there.

00:04:27.720 --> 00:04:28.600
Darling,

00:04:28.760 --> 00:04:29.640
