00:04:35.200 --> 00:04:36.640
Isn't that Man Li?

00:04:37.120 --> 00:04:38.080
I think it is.

00:04:42.320 --> 00:04:44.680
That man looks a lot like Yamamoto.

00:04:45.280 --> 00:04:47.200
What's she doing with him?

00:04:48.480 --> 00:04:49.280
Let's follow them.

00:04:49.760 --> 00:04:50.280
Come on.

00:04:53.160 --> 00:04:54.760
We're almost there.

00:05:06.160 --> 00:05:08.360
Don't worry. We'll be home in no time.

00:05:11.520 --> 00:05:12.320
Oh, darling!

00:05:21.480 --> 00:05:22.560
I think

00:05:23.040 --> 00:05:24.280
she's been drugged.

00:05:24.800 --> 00:05:25.840
Seems like it.

00:05:26.600 --> 00:05:29.000
After everything she did to you,
should we still help her?

00:05:29.920 --> 00:05:30.840
Regardless,

00:05:31.360 --> 00:05:33.120
we can't let Yamamoto
take advantage of her.

00:05:34.240 --> 00:05:34.680
Come on.

00:05:54.720 --> 00:05:56.120
Ms. Man Li,

00:05:56.520 --> 00:05:57.440
you've finally

00:05:57.680 --> 00:06:00.040
fallen into my hands.

00:06:05.640 --> 00:06:06.800
You wench!

00:06:07.480 --> 00:06:09.240
How dare you hit me!

00:06:16.160 --> 00:06:16.880
Excuse me.

00:06:17.200 --> 00:06:18.200
I'd like to ask

00:06:18.200 --> 00:06:19.720
about the room ahead…

00:06:37.840 --> 00:06:39.200
Man Li. Man Li.

00:07:30.760 --> 00:07:32.880
(What exactly
did Yamamoto give as a gift?)

00:07:50.280 --> 00:07:52.720
(No wonder Liu wasn't at dinner today.)

00:07:57.640 --> 00:07:58.160
Hey.

00:08:00.000 --> 00:08:01.280
I haven't seen Liu all day.

00:08:01.640 --> 00:08:02.360
Where is he?

00:08:02.680 --> 00:08:03.680
Is he not back yet?

00:08:04.960 --> 00:08:05.520
Oh.

00:08:05.800 --> 00:08:06.960
He went to Yamamoto's place.

00:08:06.960 --> 00:08:07.760
He's busy.

00:08:08.160 --> 00:08:10.240
To Yamamoto's? For what?

00:08:10.840 --> 00:08:13.160
Apparently,
Yamamoto prepared a hefty present.

00:08:13.160 --> 00:08:14.800
He went specifically to fetch it.

00:08:15.000 --> 00:08:15.980
What exactly is the gift?

00:08:15.990 --> 00:08:16.320
Oh,

00:08:16.320 --> 00:08:18.280
how should I know?

00:08:18.520 --> 00:08:19.920
Just wait and see.

00:08:21.760 --> 00:08:22.640
Anything else?

00:08:23.680 --> 00:08:25.080
If not, I'm going to the restroom.

00:08:56.560 --> 00:08:57.320
Zhou Musheng.

00:08:58.000 --> 00:08:59.200
The boss wants to see us.

00:09:01.720 --> 00:09:02.520
Coming.

00:09:03.280 --> 00:09:04.080
Spill it!

00:09:05.000 --> 00:09:05.800
Speak!

00:09:07.760 --> 00:09:08.680
Answer me!

00:09:09.360 --> 00:09:10.240
Speak!

00:09:11.160 --> 00:09:12.040
Or I'll kill you!

00:09:28.960 --> 00:09:29.920
Mr. Yamamoto.

00:09:30.520 --> 00:09:31.480
The goods

00:09:32.040 --> 00:09:33.120
